txt.en: Although many Haradrim marooned in Outer Gondor seek only to return to their lands in peace, there are those for whom the War cannot and will not end. You have done much to safe-guard the lands of Outer Gondor from these wicked few among the Haradrim.
Defeat many Haradrim in Outer Gondor.
